title: Excel@ Middle School (6 CDs) - Self Teach or Home School
description:
Title: Excel@ - Middle School  (c) 2000
 Company: Knowledge Adventure
    Site: www.knowledgeadventure.com
    Size: 6 CDs

-------------------------------

Description: Created by teachers, Excel@ Middle School is over 330 interactive middle-school leveled lessons for kids.  It includes 12 complete subjects covering:

1) Pre-Algebra
2) Algebra 1
3) Earth Science
4) Life Science
5) Physical Science
6) U.S. History
7) World History
8) Ancient Civilizations
9) Geography
10) Reading Comprehension
11) Grammar
12) Vocabulary

Bonus: Multimedia encyclopedia

--> Effective step-by-step method
--> Progress tracking and diagnostic tests
--> Fun and easy to use

-------------------------------

Minimum Requirements:

* Windows 95/98 (ME, XP and Vista compatible)
* Pentium 133 or faster
* 32Mb of RAM
* 20 Mb hard disk space (85Mb with encyclopedia)
* 640x480 resolution or higher (800x600 with encyclopedia)
* 256-color depth or greater (16-bit high-color for encyclopedia)
* 12x CD-ROM or higher
* 56K modem (to run internet feature)
* Windows-compatible sound card

-------------------------------

INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS:

	1) Mount/Burn using your favorite ISO mounting software
	2) Install software (To avoid problems, do NOT install the
         included version of the QuickTime software and go to the
         www.apple.com website and manually install the latest
         version of the software)
	3) Use and enjoy!
